short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Play YouTube videos sinchronized with your friends.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension lets users play YouTube videos sinchronized with other people. A user can create a room or join an existing room to play a video synchronized with other users in the room. It also allows the user to select which YouTube video tab wants to sync.
